      "chapterTitle": "一 党员的社会构成",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23669391_16_8704-8761",
          "range": "8704-8761",
          "rangeStart": 8704,
          "rangeEnd": 8761,
          "markText": "因此，在五四前后，中国都市社会集聚了一大批因就业无道、谋生乏术、前途渺茫而对社会现实产生疏离和不满情绪的知识青年。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1778509958,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-11 22:32:38",
          "chapterUid": 16,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=8704&rangeEnd=8761",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=8704&rangeEnd=8761"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "chapterTitle": "四 两不讨好",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23669391_36_6603-6800",
          "range": "6603-6800",
          "rangeStart": 6603,
          "rangeEnd": 6800,
          "markText": "萨孟武承认，国民党的社会基础是非常薄弱的。而薄弱的原因不在于国民党不想博得社会全体人民的欢心，而在于国民党太想迎合社会全体人民，结果反而一无所获。[插图]萨孟武也许在一定程度上道出了当时国民党的两难处境。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1778509951,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-11 22:32:31",
          "chapterUid": 36,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=6603&rangeEnd=6800",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=6603&rangeEnd=6800"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_36_6603-6800",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "6603-6800",
      "markText": "萨孟武承认，国民党的社会基础是非常薄弱的。而薄弱的原因不在于国民党不想博得社会全体人民的欢心，而在于国民党太想迎合社会全体人民，结果反而一无所获。萨孟武也许在一定程度上道出了当时国民党的两难处境。",
      "totalCount": 736,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=6603&rangeEnd=6800",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=6603&rangeEnd=6800"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_16_8704-8761",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "8704-8761",
      "markText": "因此，在五四前后，中国都市社会集聚了一大批因就业无道、谋生乏术、前途渺茫而对社会现实产生疏离和不满情绪的知识青年。",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=8704&rangeEnd=8761",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=8704&rangeEnd=8761"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_36_6222-6284",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "6222-6284",
      "markText": "国民党执政以后，一再声称其代表“全民”利益，而事实上，“全民”中没有哪一个阶级，真正认同或感觉到国民党确实代表了他们的利益。",
      "totalCount": 629,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=6222&rangeEnd=6284",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=6222&rangeEnd=6284"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_31_998-1047",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "998-1047",
      "markText": "国民党“不要民众”主要表现在两个方面：一是抑制、防范和禁止民众运动；二是整顿、改组和控制民众团体。",
      "totalCount": 585,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=998&rangeEnd=1047",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=998&rangeEnd=1047"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_45_8513-8561",
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "range": "8513-8561",
      "markText": "党员对党的向心力，一般源于两方面的因素：一是对党的意识形态的忠诚信仰；一是对个人现实利益的考量。",
      "totalCount": 576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=45&rangeStart=8513&rangeEnd=8561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=45&rangeStart=8513&rangeEnd=8561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_44_505-537",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "505-537",
      "markText": "简而言之，以党治国，并不是用本党的党员治国，是用本党的主义治国！",
      "totalCount": 574,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=505&rangeEnd=537",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=505&rangeEnd=537"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_60_8969-9050",
      "chapterUid": 60,
      "range": "8969-9050",
      "markText": "任何一个政党在执掌政权后，必有大批追逐名利者混进党内，同时原本纯洁的党员也容易受到权力、金钱的侵蚀而腐化。鉴此，一个富有自我革新能力的政党，一般都要定期清理门户。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=60&rangeStart=8969&rangeEnd=9050",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=60&rangeStart=8969&rangeEnd=9050"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_13_7236-7288",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "7236-7288",
      "markText": "大约从这时起，苏俄开始提醒孙中山不要执着于单纯的武装革命，而应该注意健全党的组织和重视思想政治宣传工作。",
      "totalCount": 546,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=7236&rangeEnd=7288",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=7236&rangeEnd=7288"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_14_14229-14282",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "14229-14282",
      "markText": "孙中山对中国老百姓的政治文化素质一直持悲观态度。他把国人分成“先知先觉”、“后知后觉”和“不知不觉”三类。",
      "totalCount": 544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14229&rangeEnd=14282",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14229&rangeEnd=14282"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_14_1322-1380",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1322-1380",
      "markText": "1921年底，孙中山在广西会见马林时，宣称马克思主义里面没有什么新的东西，中国的经典学说早在两千年前就都已经说过了。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1322&rangeEnd=1380",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1322&rangeEnd=1380"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_26_945-1044",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "945-1044",
      "markText": "1930年，以阎锡山、冯玉祥为代表的地方实力派，联合以汪精卫、陈公博为代表的改组派，和以邹鲁、谢持为代表的西山会议派，形成反蒋势力大联合，先在北平召开会议另立党统，进而发动了一场规模浩大的中原大战。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=945&rangeEnd=1044",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=945&rangeEnd=1044"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_52_1875-1952",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "1875-1952",
      "markText": "国民党不大注重培养党员成为社会各界的楷模，以赢得民众的信仰和拥护，而是网罗社会各界既有的权势精英加入国民党，进而达到渗透和控制社会各界和各阶层民众的目的。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23669391&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1875&rangeEnd=1952",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03232c2071692a8f0326851?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1875&rangeEnd=1952"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23669391_14_13666-13753",
      "chapterUid": 14,
